        "mainbody": "'''Klim Jhasso''' was a minor noble of the [[Jhasso (family)|Jhasso]] family in [[Baldur's Gate]] in the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]].",
        "History": "In the {{YearlinkName|1494}}, the Jhasso family was on the verge of bankruptcy as their trading coster was struggling and they had very little money. To add more bad luck, Klim was abducted while walking in the [[Baldur's Gate/Lower City|Lower City]] of Baldur's Gate by [[Dead Three]] cultists. While imprisoned within the cult's lair in the city, he was tortured by [[Ygnath]] while [[Kazzira]] watched."
